server Creation - Nodejs + express

basic commands
---------------

1)Creating package .json - npm init
2)Creating node modules - npm i express(Install express)
3)Install nodemon - npm install -g nodemon
4)Run - nodemon index.js


basic steps
==============
1)Create a  folder(Bankserver)
2)create package.json file
3)install express
4)import express inside the index.js file
5)create an app using express
6)setup the port nuber
7)Resolving http request

9)jwt token
Install jwt token - npm i jsonwebtoken
to generate token - sign()

10) middleware - it comes in the middle of the request and response cycle of the Node js execution
      req,reg,next
   
   1)Application specific application - for enteire application
   2)  Router specific middleware - for token verification we use verify()

   13) asynchronous function resolving - Promise
      1)Resolve state - .then()
      2) Reject State -  catch()

 14) Cors - CRoss origin resource sharing
  
       install cors - npm i cors